Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:33.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NOff to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:42.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NGood morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:44.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NOh... good morning, Futaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:46.05,Main,,0,0,0,,...how are... you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:49.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm doing great...\NThank you so much for asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:55.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NIt's gorgeous out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.10,Main,,0,0,0,,But on the forecast,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:00:58.85,Main,,0,0,0,,they said there's a good\Nchance of rain this afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:00:59.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:01.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm super bummed about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:04.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, that hurts.\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:05.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:06.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You... are behaving\Nvery strangely...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:08.40,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:11.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... what's wrong with me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:13.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the one who's\Nacting weird, Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:15.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.12,0:01:17.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWait up. Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:20.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Man, I am definitely gonna\Nfall asleep in class...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:22.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I almost slept through my alarm,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,so it's lucky I'm even\Ngoing to school at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:28.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Heh. Well, I had to skip\Nbreakfast, but we can't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:31.26,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:32.84,Main,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.93,0:01:35.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Game's up...\NI know what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:36.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NWhat what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:37.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I've heard of\Nthese pranks before...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.89,0:01:39.52,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a hidden\Ncamera type of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:41.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You've had your fun...\Nbut that's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:43.94,Main,,0,0,0,,As they say "the jig is up."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:45.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:47.94,Main,,0,0,0,,How long did you think you\Nwould be able to fool me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:50.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Your acting skills leave a\Nlot to be desired, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:52.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:53.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama, I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:56.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Why's Yoko acting\Nso strangely...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:57.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think she's sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Should we get help?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:00.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NI'm not being weird, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:04.71,Main,,0,0,0,,It took two months,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:06.46,Main,,0,0,0,,but I finished crocheting\Nmy lace yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:08.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!\NDo you want to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:10.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a\Nwaste of time to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:13.63,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want lace so bad,\Nthen just buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:15.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NAw... Don't tease me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:16.84,Main,,0,0,0,,you know this is my hobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:18.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at it. Isn't it the cutest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:20.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Nope, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:22.02,Main,,0,0,0,,that's the lamest hobby ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:23.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:25.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Why're you hiding?\NIs something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:26.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NSo even when I'm not around,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:28.11,Main,,0,0,0,,they're still like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:30.32,Main,,0,0,0,,What is going on with those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:31.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:34.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NUm... Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:36.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I was wondering...\Num... I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:41.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Jeez, spit it out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:42.66,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... you haven't\Nturned the worksheet in yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I've collected everybody\Nelse's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:50.34,Main,,0,0,0,,...and... since I have to give\Nthem to the teacher all at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:51.71,Main,,0,0,0,,can I have yours, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:52.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:54.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I forgot\Nto do it, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:57.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don'tcha just take\Ncare of it for me, kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Since you're class rep and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:01.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NUh! But... I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:04.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NAh. I get it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:05.73,Main,,0,0,0,,This is all just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:08.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You should turn it in so\NNishiyama can do her job
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,and you don't get in trouble\Nwith the teacher... Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:12.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:14.78,Main,,0,0,0,,You look like\Nyou're about to cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:18.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWhat an awful, awful dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NI hate Hayama so much...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:24.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate her, I hate\Nher, I hate her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.58,Main,,0,0,0,,She's a\Ngood-for-nothin' troublemaker
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:26.96,Main,,0,0,0,,who doesn't care about\Nanyone but herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.71,Main,,0,0,0,,and one of these days,\Nshe's gonna pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll teach her to\Ntreat me with respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.46,Main,,0,0,0,,She's different, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NThat's enough slacking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Look how upset\Nyou've made Nishiyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:39.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Now hurry up and\Nturn your work in already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:40.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Calm down, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:41.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:42.64,Main,,0,0,0,,You should be nicer to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:45.43,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like she's class rep\Nbecause she wants to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Nobody else felt like\Nhaving all the extra work
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:49.94,Main,,0,0,0,,and responsibility,\Nso poor, timid Nishiyama
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:50.94,Main,,0,0,0,,got stuck with the job...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:52.11,Main,,0,0,0,,She can't speak up for herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:54.90,Main,,0,0,0,,so when the teacher asked,\Nshe just agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess nothing\Nwill change the way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.66,Main,,0,0,0,,those two feel about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:09.50,Main,,0,0,0,,So tired...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:11.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I could take a nap right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:12.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't do that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:14.96,Main,,0,0,0,,If you fall asleep now,\Nyou'll miss afternoon classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NJust five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:19.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NThis is too strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:22.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know how\Nlong I can take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:23.89,Main,,0,0,0,,They probably\Naren't the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:25.26,Main,,0,0,0,,who are different...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:27.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what everyone\Nelse is like in this dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Whee...! I hate\Nthe world so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:34.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It's full of nothing\Nbut anger and despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:35.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should\Njust take this bat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.78,Main,,0,0,0,,and break all the\Nwindows in the school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Or I could steal a motorcycle,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:42.07,Main,,0,0,0,,except I don't know how to drive\None so I'd probably just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:43.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:45.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, your sister\Nis always getting
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:46.70,Main,,0,0,0,,into all kinds of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:48.20,Main,,0,0,0,,She's got such a bad girl\Nstreak, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:50.62,Main,,0,0,0,,She totally knows\Nhow to let loose,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:52.75,Main,,0,0,0,,unlike some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:00.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that...? Yamaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:01.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Nishikawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that how you\Naddress a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:13.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so shocked,\NI don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:17.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Have you lost your mind...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:19.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You just punched a teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, whoops... My hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Nyou just did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:25.53,Main,,0,0,0,,And as a matter of fact,\NI didn't punch him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:27.08,Main,,0,0,0,,That was clearly a slap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.66,Main,,0,0,0,,There is a difference, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what we're\Ngonna focus on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Inexcusable...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:34.21,Main,,0,0,0,,That kind of violence\Nis not tolerated here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Report to the principal's\Noffice immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:39.05,Main,,0,0,0,,If somebody has a problem,\Nthey're welcome to come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] You're only getting\Nyourself into more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:41.97,Main,,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to stop! This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:47.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Now, now...\NWhat's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:52.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NClass will be starting soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:54.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Return to your rooms at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:57.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Unless what\Nyou really want--is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:05:59.44,Main,,0,0,0,,...to experience the\Nkind of punishment
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:01.94,Main,,0,0,0,,only Ms. Shino can offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:09.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] That's it.\NThat's where it ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Such a good dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:11.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NYou call that a good dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:13.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Where do you come up\Nwith these things...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows\Nhow nice I am to Yamaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I would never mistreat\Nhim in such a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:19.42,Main,,0,0,0,,No... 'course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Too bad I woke up right\Nat the best part...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe if I try really hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I can have the same\Ndream again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:26.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I hafta say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:28.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not a big fan of\Nthe way I came off in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:30.35,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a dream, nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You were weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.18,Main,,0,0,0,,but I wasn't too\Ndifferent from the real me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Least I wasn't violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you were\Neven in the dream, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:37.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,That was obviously me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:41.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NIt does sound kinda fun
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:43.90,Main,,0,0,0,,to be a different version\Nof yourself, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:45.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Especially for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:47.62,Main,,0,0,0,,since you're usually hiding\Nyour real personality, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh, heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:52.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[SAKURA] Oh, there you are...!\NWait up, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:54.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NSakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:56.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[SAKURA]\NWell, what do you think...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:59.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't it awesome?\NI gave myself a total makeover!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.21,Main,,0,0,0,,You look adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:02.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:03.26,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what I was going for,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.22,Main,,0,0,0,,and I think I totally\Nnailed it, too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:07.97,Main,,0,0,0,,So... you know how I'm\Ngonna be a famous pop idol
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:09.39,Main,,0,0,0,,when I grow up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:10.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:11.72,Main,,0,0,0,,How could we forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:13.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe you could\Nlisten to one of my songs
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:15.60,Main,,0,0,0,,if you're not busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to practice\Nsinging in front of people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:19.48,Main,,0,0,0,,so I don't get stage fright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:22.82,Main,,0,0,0,,So young and pretty,\Nlike a flower in the spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.57,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to keep me,\Nyou'd better buy a ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:29.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know how lucky you\Nare to have me in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.41,Main,,0,0,0,,My love will pierce\Nyou like the sharpest knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:34.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You must know that someday,\NI will be your wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.96,Main,,0,0,0,,You will never look at another\Ngirl for as long as you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:40.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NUgh... my poor ears...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:43.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Compared\Nto the way this girl sings,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:46.42,Main,,0,0,0,,my sister's actually on key.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NPlease... you gotta stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:51.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] You might want to\Npractice a little more alone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:53.76,Main,,0,0,0,,before performing\Nin front of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:55.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NYeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard once that if you're\Ntone-deaf you can put
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:57.89,Main,,0,0,0,,a bucket over your\Nhead and it'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:07:59.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NDo that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:04.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NOh-kay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NShe's really doing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[SAKURA]\NI found a bucket...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:12.16,Main,,0,0,0,,So I sing like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:13.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NYeah... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:17.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never really\Nseen it done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:19.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[SAKURA]\NSo young and pretty, like--!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:27.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[SAKURA]\NSo young and pretty, like a--!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:32.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[SAKURA]\NI'm... not so sure about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:34.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I might throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:37.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Good thing\Nwe have a bucket then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NI don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:47.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I tried to do it\Nlike Sakura had hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey...! I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:52.28,Main,,0,0,0,,How about like this? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:54.83,Main,,0,0,0,,This would keep it from getting\Nin my way all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:55.91,Main,,0,0,0,,It's missing something,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.58,Main,,0,0,0,,but I can't put\Nmy finger on what...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh I got it...! Glasses, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:00.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Glasses aren't some\Nkind of requirement
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:03.21,Main,,0,0,0,,for wearing braids, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Hmmm... Maybe I should\Nstop trying different styles
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.34,Main,,0,0,0,,and just cut it shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would you do\Nsomething like that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:11.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Cutting your gorgeous\Nlocks would be a tragedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:14.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I think it might\Nmake for a nice change...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:15.10,Main,,0,0,0,,and with all these split-ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:16.51,Main,,0,0,0,,it would look a\Nlot healthier, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:18.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, long hair\Nrequires a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.85,Main,,0,0,0,,of shampoo and conditioner,\Nand that can get expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.52,Main,,0,0,0,,No...! You can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:27.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Just think of all the years\Nof effort that will be wasted
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.32,Main,,0,0,0,,if you cut it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, you've been\Ngrowing your hair out ever
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.28,Main,,0,0,0,,since you were a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:32.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NYamaji's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:33.74,Main,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:34.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhat if you cut it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.58,Main,,0,0,0,,and then you didn't\Nlike how it looked?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I've always thought your hair\Nwas pretty much perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:40.71,Main,,0,0,0,,so, you don't need to\Nchange a thing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:42.12,Main,,0,0,0,,You really think it suits me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:43.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Even girls who used\Nto be rich like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.04,Main,,0,0,0,,can always rock\Na princess haircut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:49.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Does what actually looks\Ngood factor in anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:52.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Thanks for coming.\NHave a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:00.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got this down...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you think I've honed\Nmy skills as a cashier...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:04.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd consider myself a\Nprofessional at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] You're\Nabsolutely magnificent...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.11,Main,,0,0,0,,The best in the world\Nat anything you do...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:11.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Definitely a professional!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:14.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NYeah it's very... impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:16.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... I was shocked when she\Ngot a job in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:19.12,Main,,0,0,0,,so I guess I should\Nbe impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.00,Main,,0,0,0,,She's like a flower\Nthat grows quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:23.87,Main,,0,0,0,,when watered with\Npraise and adoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:26.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[HIYORI] Look, here it is...!\NWe found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.84,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the shop\NI was telling you about,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:29.67,Main,,0,0,0,,the one from the flyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[bell chimes]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:34.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome! How can I\Nhelp you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:36.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:39.51,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.43,Main,,0,0,0,,They all look so yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:49.82,Main,,0,0,0,,What's up? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:53.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[inaudible]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:59.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[SEI]\NNishikawa...? Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:14.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NA school friend... from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:17.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It's nice to see you, Osakabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh! You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:21.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. I do, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:24.48,Main,,0,0,0,,We were in the same grade\Nat my previous school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Ooh... Mannenro\NGirls' Academy, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:29.77,Main,,0,0,0,,The school where\Nall the rich girls go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that rich girls\Nhad after-school jobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:36.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait... are you doing it\Nto learn about the real world?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:39.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Actually... my\Ncircumstances changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:42.45,Main,,0,0,0,,and I'm not what anyone\Nwould call a rich girl now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I took this job because\NI really needed the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:49.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWe have a large selection,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:52.13,Main,,0,0,0,,but these two cakes are our\Nseasonal recommendations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:54.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[HIYORI] Great.\NI'll take one of each, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You're right, Yamaji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:57.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:12:00.22,Main,,0,0,0,,that was more professional\Nin my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:05.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:09.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[SEI] You can give me\Na call if you'd like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:10.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's my number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:12.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy to help\Nif you ever need it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.57,Main,,0,0,0,,so please feel free\Nto get in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Keep up the hard work,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.12,Main,,0,0,0,,and I'm sure\Neverything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:22.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming.\NHave a nice day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NMiss Yoko, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:29.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NTake it easy for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:30.92,Main,,0,0,0,,You were amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:34.13,Main,,0,0,0,,A total professional!\NNo one could have done better!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, it couldn't\Nhave been easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Only an amateur would\Nlet something like
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:39.68,Main,,0,0,0,,that trip them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:44.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I don't know why\Nyou all seem so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:46.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm a\Nprofessional...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:47.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Nothing is\Nmore important to you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.31,Main,,0,0,0,,than your pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.98,Main,,0,0,0,,but you didn't even flinch\Nwhen it was threatened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:52.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Now... if you will excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I believe I will\Ntake a short break...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:57.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit thirsty,\Nso I could use a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:12:59.90,Main,,0,0,0,,That's mayonnaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:03.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Heard you had\Na rough day yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:07.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It wasn't so awful, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:09.50,Main,,0,0,0,,It is difficult to have\Npeople from my former life
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.29,Main,,0,0,0,,see my reduced circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:14.34,Main,,0,0,0,,but the fact is, I can't\Ngo back to being who I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:19.13,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the person I am now,\Nand I think I can accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:21.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's mature!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:22.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NGood morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:26.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't the weather\Ntoday beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:28.98,Main,,0,0,0,,So bright and sunshiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:30.89,Main,,0,0,0,,So what's new?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:32.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, that hurts.\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:35.07,Main,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what\Nyou did to her in the dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:37.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[SAKURA]\NYou're such a slob!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:39.74,Main,,0,0,0,,You need more feminine charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:40.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:41.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.53,Main,,0,0,0,,For starters, you're\Nshoveling food into your face
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:46.12,Main,,0,0,0,,like a starving monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:48.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I spend half the day\Nwith a bucket on my head
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:50.08,Main,,0,0,0,,because I'm committed\Nto my dream...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:53.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should try putting\Neffort into something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you believe\Nshe said that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:57.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:59.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I never realized\Nthat I was lacking
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:00.88,Main,,0,0,0,,in the feminine\Ncharm department...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:02.59,Main,,0,0,0,,So I decided that\NI would prove to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.68,0:14:04.80,Main,,0,0,0,,how dainty and girly I can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:05.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Tee-hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.64,Main,,0,0,0,,You've really\Ninspired me, Miss Yoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to work\Njust as hard as you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:11.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I know you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:16.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Cute...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:19.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at the pretty little\Nbirdies having a nice chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:22.99,Main,,0,0,0,,You're breaking\Nout in spots all over...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I think you have hives!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:28.78,Main,,0,0,0,,These are really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:29.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they sure are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:30.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You want a piece, Odagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:34.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate the\Ngenerous offer, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Tee-hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:41.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NUh... are you feeling okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should go\Nto the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.30,Main,,0,0,0,,It's almost lunchtime...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have\Nsweets right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NYou sure you don't want one...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:50.76,Main,,0,0,0,,They're burnt milk caramels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:54.18,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Really, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NYou know you're drooling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:59.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO] So... you don't\Nthink you're girly enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.65,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for pointers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.69,Main,,0,0,0,,that's something I should be\Nable to help you out with...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:05.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I maintain a strict beauty\Nregimen, and it does wonders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah? What kinda\Nstuff do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:08.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I take rose supplements
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,and wear perfume to keep\Nmyself smelling nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:13.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I do stretches to keep\Nmyself limber and flexible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:15.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I do crunches and leg-lifts--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.25,Main,,0,0,0,,which keeps my figure\Ntrim and well-toned...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:20.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I moisturize and exfoliate and\Ndo the occasional chemical peel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:21.96,Main,,0,0,0,,How do you find\Ntime to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Amazing...! You must spend hours
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:26.01,Main,,0,0,0,,every day trying to\Nimprove your appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:27.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah... I want\Nto better myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:30.14,Main,,0,0,0,,You got a problem with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NMy lucky number is three...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.23,Main,,0,0,0,,My lucky color is yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:35.89,Main,,0,0,0,,What is that, your horoscope?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,That's pretty girly,\Nisn't it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I heard before\Nthat girls like looking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:40.82,Main,,0,0,0,,at their horoscopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:42.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWe sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:43.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAJIME]\NHey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be stopping\Nby Mr. Stuffed's for sure today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:47.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:48.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you\Nhaven't heard about
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.41,Main,,0,0,0,,his new yellow\Ncurry challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:52.70,Main,,0,0,0,,All you gotta do is eat three\Nkilos and your meal is free!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:55.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Yellow! And three?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA, YOKO]\NJust let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.50,Main,,0,0,0,,No... I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:15:59.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAJIME]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:01.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think I\Ncould ever finish
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,three kilograms\Nof food at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:04.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a dainty little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:07.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAJIME] What are you doing,\Ntrying to make a fool of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:08.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You're Futaba Odagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:10.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't give up on a challenge\Nwithout even trying...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:14.39,Main,,0,0,0,,It's disrespectful to all\Nthose who have lost to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:22.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Just be yourself...\NGo stuff your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:23.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I second that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:25.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I think the best version\Nof you is the one
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.40,Main,,0,0,0,,that's smiling the brightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:30.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA gasping]\NOkay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:37.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:40.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Feminine charm level: zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:41.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NThanks for the grub. See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:44.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAJIME] One of these\Ndays, I'll beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:48.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] Futaba! I heard you were\Ntrying to become more girly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:49.88,Main,,0,0,0,,How's it going so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NUh... well... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.93,Main,,0,0,0,,After Teru told me about\Nit, I made this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NStop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:57.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want any soup made
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,from scary, disgusting,\Nunpronounceable ingredients!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:01.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not soup...\NSee, it's a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:06.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] I think you're\Nmissing the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:08.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:10.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NDrink up... Better you than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:12.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I brought enough for everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:18.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU] What happened?\NYou look different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:21.21,Main,,0,0,0,,You think it worked?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:23.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Have our feminine charm\Nlevels really increased?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:25.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I didn't think\Nthat we had plans
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.63,Main,,0,0,0,,to meet up today... did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU] I just had\Nsomething to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:31.01,Main,,0,0,0,,My dad said he has\Na job for your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:32.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?! He's going\Nto hire my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:35.14,Main,,0,0,0,,That's awesome!\NI'm so happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:37.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's gonna want\Nsomething in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:39.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you so, so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know how\NI can ever repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:43.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU gasps]\NOh, I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:47.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe you could sign a marriage\Napplication or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:48.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, y'know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:50.49,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like it would be real\Nor anything, just for fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:51.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Like playing pretend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey... that sounds\Nlike a great game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:56.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go play right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:57.62,Main,,0,0,0,,If anyone needs us,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:59.87,Main,,0,0,0,,we'll be submitting\Nour marriage application.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:02.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:04.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[SAKURA] Did you know I've\Nbeen practicing my singing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:06.59,Main,,0,0,0,,--You wanna hear some?\N--[YU] No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:09.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[SAKURA] So young and\Npretty, like a flower...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:10.84,Main,,0,0,0,,He's a pushy little guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:14.05,Main,,0,0,0,,But I don't think he stands\Na chance against Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I am Yoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:21.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Daughter of the\NNishikawa family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.81,Main,,0,0,0,,My father will soon\Nbe gainfully employed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.27,Main,,0,0,0,,at a respectable company.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:26.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NHow fantastically normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:30.61,Main,,0,0,0,,This is going to change\Neverything for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't have to be such\Na miser or salivate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:34.11,Main,,0,0,0,,over every little scrap of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[SASAME]\NUm... hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I kinda have\Nsomething for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:41.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a gift... from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:43.33,Main,,0,0,0,,For the Valentine's chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:44.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:46.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[SASAME] I had a hard time\Ndeciding what to get...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:48.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought cookies\Nwould be a good idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:50.38,Main,,0,0,0,,but I wanted the gift\Nto be useful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean... They're mine?\NThey're all for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:53.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's our Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.09,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll take her some\Ntime to adjust.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:58.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Hold on...\NIsn't White Day next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:00.22,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:07.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Still thinking about\Nthem, aren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:09.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I know, I am absolutely\Npitiful, aren't I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:11.53,Main,,0,0,0,,How long have we\Nbeen friends now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:15.07,Main,,0,0,0,,and I haven't changed a bit\Nsince the day I met you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:17.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?\NYou've changed a ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:18.95,Main,,0,0,0,,You really think I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:20.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what\Nyou said when we met?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:23.04,Main,,0,0,0,,"I don't recall asking\Nyou to join me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:24.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Honestly, how rude!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:28.17,Main,,0,0,0,,You sounded just like\Na stereotypical rich girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.96,Main,,0,0,0,,A rare and dangerous species...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:31.46,Main,,0,0,0,,So special!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:32.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.42,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you even talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:36.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you mean endangered species?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:38.51,Main,,0,0,0,,...is that what they call it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:40.26,Main,,0,0,0,,when there aren't\Nvery many left of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:41.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand why
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:44.73,Main,,0,0,0,,we're talking about animals\Nall of a sudden... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:46.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, do they call\Nthem endangered
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:48.48,Main,,0,0,0,,'cause they're in\Ndanger of going extinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's why it's so\Nimportant to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:52.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:54.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I honestly don't get what\Nthis has to do with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:59.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Uh! Another\Nendangered species!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:00.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:01.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NGood thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:02.87,Main,,0,0,0,,The world doesn't need\Nany more of those in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:05.00,Main,,0,0,0,,The world doesn't need\Nany more of what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:06.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure they were\Ntalking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Me, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:10.34,Main,,0,0,0,,That species is already\Nbeing protected, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,...by Kondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NWhy are you wearing that again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:17.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:18.76,Main,,0,0,0,,A strange and fearsome beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think we should\Nget too close to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:21.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonobe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:23.72,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon! We need to\Nget out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I hear they'll charge\Nif you make eye contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:29.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NAnother one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:32.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] This one's poisonous...\NBeware its venom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:34.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:39.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Where are you going...?\NWait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:45.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWhat's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:52.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:51.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NI thought you should know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:53.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I am graduating\Nfrom bread crusts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA, FUTABA]\NYeah...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:56.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Today I thought I would try
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.25,0:22:58.21,Main,,0,0,0,,a bowl of instant\N{\i1}yakisoba{\i0} noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:00.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA, FUTABA]\NWow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:04.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.88,0:23:07.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NNo... I couldn't stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:10.60,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all over now. She\Nput the sauce in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:15.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't eat it like that...!\NIt's a total noodle fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:16.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:21.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NAww, look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.48,0:23:23.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NShe's so cute when she pouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NI don't care if they're ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.61,0:23:26.28,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like I enjoy\Ninstant noodles, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.36,0:23:28.24,Main,,0,0,0,,They're such a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.79,0:23:33.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Bread crusts are\Ninexpensive, abundant,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.33,0:23:34.12,Main,,0,0,0,,and delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NYou brought some?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.17,0:23:40.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NMm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:43.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.01,0:23:48.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
